# clang-format config for signalwire-cpp.
#
# Source-style ONLY: this gate is wire/surface-neutral by construction —
# reformatting whitespace/line-breaks cannot change the enumerated public
# surface (the libclang signature enumerator + the regex surface walker both
# normalise to the symbol/shape, not the layout) nor the FunctionResult
# emission. Verified during rollout: port_signatures.json + port_surface.json
# stay byte-identical and EMISSION stays green across a full reformat.
#
# Google base (the canonical, widely-tooled C++ style — no bikeshedding),
# with a 100-col limit to match the existing codebase's wider lines and keep
# the diff mechanical rather than a re-wrap storm. Vendored deps/ are NEVER
# formatted (the fmt gate scopes clang-format to src/ + include/ + tools/).
BasedOnStyle: Google
ColumnLimit: 100
